  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*single-state TQ-residual check on a non-symmetric rep: each Q_k (built from QSolve3) must be\n  annihilated by BaxOp, tested at several generic numeric u. State: λ1={2,1,0}, λ2={1,0,0}\n  (adjoint⊗fund), (H1,H2,n)=(1,0,0) (confirmed a valid n=0 key of TauEigensystem3[{2,1,0},{1,0,0}]).*)\nModule[{λ1 = {2, 1, 0}, λ2 = {1, 0, 0}, H1 = 1, H2 = 0, n = 0, res},\n  res = Table[\n     Max@Table[\n        Abs@Chop[N[BaxOp[λ1, λ2][H1, H2, n][Function[uu, Qfun[λ1, λ2][H1, H2, n][k][uu]]][u0], 30]],\n        {u0, {2/3, 9/5, 4, 23/7}}],\n     {k, 1, 3}];\n  If[Max[res] > 10^-10, Print[\"TQ RESIDUAL FAIL: \", res]; Abort[]];\n  {\"perQresidual\" -> res}\n]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352974\" data-output-id=\"426\" data-out-n=\"105\" data-sub-idx=\"1\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"37\" data-sub-start=\"3\" data-sub-end=\"11\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[105]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrpc8oba-8dmdswh\" data-page-width-em=\"50\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0e3BlclFyZXNpZHVhbH1cdG8gXGxlZnRcezAsMCwwXHJpZ2h0XH1ccmlnaHRcfQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">perQresidual</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
